as: practice and theory. In: Proceedings of the 2003 Conference on Designing for User Experiences (2003)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Pruitt%2C%20J.%2C%20Grudin%2C%20J.%3A%20Personas%3A%20practice%20and%20theory.%20In%3A%20Proceedings%20of%20the%202003%20Conference%20on%20Designing%20for%20User%20Experiences%20%282003%29\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">47.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR47\">Carroll, J.M.: Scenario-based design: envisioning work and technology in system development. Wiley, New York (1995)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Scenario-based%20design%3A%20envisioning%20work%20and%20technology%20in%20system%20development&amp;author=JM.%20Carroll&amp;publication_year=1995\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">48.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR48\">Wenger, E.: Communities of Practice: Learning, Meaning, and Identity. Cambridge University Press, Cambridge (1998)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceDOI\"><a class=\"gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"CrossRef\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1017/CBO9780511803932\"><span><span>CrossRef</span></span></a></span><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Communities%20of%20Practice%3A